name: "URBAN GROZA": HΞN Limited Edition
description: To the lost generation, brought up in the slums of panel blocks. Abandoned yards - their playgrounds. The streets - a circulatory system. Someone failed along the way. They can't get rid of the memories of the past. There is no future. This is a HΞN reference to my original Instagram artwork. Only 5 copies exist - you get the original. No regrets.
